data.description: Charming all brick rancher in Apple Country with tons of potential and just waiting for your finishing touches! Front and rear covered porches allow you to enjoy the views and level 1.53 acre lot.  Spacious dining area adjoining the kitchen makes this home great for entertaining even with the largest number of guests, Kitchen offers tons of cabinetry and natural light.  Custom pine mouldings made right here at the local sawmill!  New LVP flooring in Living Room and Kitchen.  Finished basement could be the ultimate Man Cave or Recreation Room.  A separate set of stairs from the basement leads up to the attached 2 car attached garage.  There you will find the updated 200 Amp electric service with plenty of room for any future projects.  Calling all nature lovers and history buffs, Appalachian trail 5 miles away with tons of streams and lakes for fishing, Gettysburg Battlefield 14 miles, Sight and Sound Theater 55 miles, 35 miles to Hershey Park, Carlisle where famous car shows take place is 15 miles and lastly Harrisburg is only 24 miles away!
